🌅✨ “Golden hour, endless waves.”
Elara stands on a cliffside beach in Puglia, Italy, sundress flowing in the warm breeze. Her dog explores nearby while a local guide points out the horizon. Sunlight bathes the scene in golden tones, waves glistening below — cinematic, vibrant, and unforgettable. 📸🐾
